% solution of the large firm's problem  \Ep{oli9}  in the form:
% $$ \left[\matrix{z_{t+1} \cr \mu_{x,t+1}\cr}\right]
%    = \left[\matrix{m_{11} & m_{12} \cr
%                    m_{21} & m_{22}\cr}\right]
%      \left[\matrix{z_t \cr \mu_{x,t} \cr} \right]  \EQN oli11 $$
